{"title": "Israel in Europe", "description": "G. F. Abbott delivers a complete historical review of the Jewish peoples in the European continent from the third century BC and up to the early XX century.  Topics such as Jewish customs, culture, successes, resilience, persecution, survival, integration, marginalization, homeland, and \u201cthe Jewish question\u201d, are explored in detail.  This work is so thorough that it has become a mandatory resource for those interested in Jewish history in Europe.  - Summary by mpinedag", "duration": 69432, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "14674", "name": "George Frederick Abbott"}], "coverArt": null, "copyright_year": "1907", "genres": ["History", "Other religions"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "mpinedag"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "mpinedag"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "gracesilvey"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Introduction", "readers": [3796], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/israelineurope_2603_librivox/israelineurope_00_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 636}, {"section": 1, "title": "Chapter I. Hebraism and Hellenism, part 1", "readers": [3796], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/israelineurope_2603_librivox/israelineurope_01_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1132}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter I. Hebraism and Hellenism, part 2", "readers": [3796], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/israelineurope_2603_librivox/israelineurope_02_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1159}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter II. The Jew in the Roman Empire", "readers": [3796], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/israelineurope_2603_librivox/israelineurope_03_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1271}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter III. Judaism and Paganism", "readers": [3796], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/israelineurope_2603_librivox/israelineurope_04_abbott_64kb.mp3", "duration": 742}, {"section": 5, "title": "C